---
title: Thyme Beef Rump & Parsnip Mash with Caramelised Cherry Tomatoes
description: Get creative with the classic steak and mash by adding caramelised cherry tomatoes, resting in a buttery thyme sauce. Trust us, it's the seared beef rump's new best friend! Stacked with nutritious greens and a smooth parsnip mash, it’s bound to beat all your dinnertime cravings.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thyme-beef-rump-a060e973.jpg
